skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: A skill built for the Amazon Alexa flash briefing to read the headlines of Eastside Humor's site. This news is entirely satirical in nature. Any portrayals of specific people, companies, or places are all coincidental or false.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
